http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/karnataka/Seminar-for-MBA-aspirants-tomorrow/article14009150.ece

The Hindu and Hyderabad-based Institute of Public Enterprises will conduct a seminar titled ‘Emerge MBA 2016’ for students who wish to pursue MBA courses in premium management institutes.It will be held on January 21 at the Hyderabad Karnataka Chamber of Commerce and Industry auditorium from 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. The entry is free.InteractionEminent speakers from the Institute of Public Enterprise will guide students for MBA entrance tests and also provide them an opportunity to interact with the faculty there.